To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private AverageDirectionalMovementIndexRating _adxr;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_adxr = ADXR(symbol, period);

// In OnData()
if (_adxr.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "adx", _adxr.ADX.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "averagedirectionalmovementindexrating", _adxr.Current.Value);
}
# In Initialize()
symbol = self.AddEquity("SPY").Symbol
self.adxr = self.ADXR(symbol, period)

# In OnData()
if self.adxr.IsReady:
    self.Plot("My Indicators", "adx", self.adxr.ADX.Current.Value)
    self.Plot("My Indicators", "averagedirectionalmovementindexrating", self.adxr.Current.Value)
